MIAMI-DADE COUNTY and City of Miami, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Ofelia PEREZ, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-0537, 3D18-0533 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 26, 2018

ORDERED that appellants' notice of voluntary dismissal is recognized by the Court, and these consolidated appeals from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida are hereby dismissed.
